{"tid":1867983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫護就是勇武] 現在勇武退下來了 和理非可以接力嗎?","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T17:12:51.000Z","uid":225100,"like":67,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53d07fa4b266aa3df40caad780683e4c3525ffa4","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>半年反送中</strong><br />\n成日想勇武退場等和理非接力<br />\n終於勇武拉咗一大堆 打殘一堆 被消失又一堆 清算未齊停過<br />\n逼於無奈轉晒地下 只能處於半退場狀態<br />\n他們的犧牲換來<br />\n法案正式撤回<br />\n區議會大勝<br />\n人權法通過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但其餘訴求仍然未見其踪</span><br />\n<br />\n依加個天整個肺炎畀支那<br />\n雖然燒埋香港人<br />\n但講咗半年嘅罷工總算踏出咗第一步<br />\n<code>大人肯罷工 細路唔洗衝</code><br />\n<br />\n<strong>到依加罷工</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">醫護就係當時嘅勇武 就如612金鍾 71衝入立法 一直走在最前嘅嗰班人</span><br />\n依加醫護決定復工(退場)<br />\n要爭取嘅全面封關只係階段性勝利 尤如半年黎嘅反送中<br />\n但醫護的確開咗個頭 示範畀大家睇咩叫罷工<br />\n然而疫情日益嚴重 醫護復工的決定我是尊重的 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而我亦相信 罷工醫護由其是幾位主席必定如勇武一樣將會遭到邪惡政權的清算</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其他工會(和理非) 係唔係有責任出黎接力 <br />\n出黎話畀醫護手足聽一星期嘅努力沒有白費呢?</span><br />\n<br />\n<code>光復香港 時代革命</code><br />\n唔係一句口號<br />\n而係香港人以行動去實踐 再達成嘅目標<br />\n<br />\n現在迷霧里最遠處吹來了號角聲<br />\n你願意來齊集這里 來全力抗對<br />\n來接力繼續去光復香港嗎?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">好 我同其他工會接力 醫護手足辛苦了</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">不了 醫護on9咁都復工 冇得畀我Freeride</span>"},{"pid":"c08c14b38275eb023be498696715ea6d7aa6b1e2","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再Freeride<br />\n唔想再被condom了<br />\n香港人 一次咁多<br />\n團結 一齊罷好唔好?"},{"pid":"1f3ca69fdfd187d542c5dac619801aae31ebff0a","tid":1867983,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529a9188037a24a27a35fc7339bc875afc3b696e","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:03:11.000Z","msg":"首咩當其衝<br />\n你老母係<span style=\"color: gold;\">唇亡齒寒</span>阿<br />\n大家一條船架"},{"pid":"2af1c18e600803dab44289f486460d8847d88e3e","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"唔係隔離<br />\n唔係咁多豁免<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全面封關啊</span>"},{"pid":"862844a26a3db22553ffeadb47cf5ead17cbbc96","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3ca69fdfd187d542c5dac619801aae31ebff0a","tid":1867983,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dcb20037227f29f924bfb5e05721f769df7b03","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"醫護就係當時612嘅勇武<br />\n多謝醫護<br />\n多謝勇武<br />\n<br />\n到我哋接力了"},{"pid":"7b4993f23903f2de9cac5c6f5fe1b19ecb551c83","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65d7836309fa39a3cf3bd566b2fb0b67a48f8d","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8fb93a9700341ca9aa7d03f49d7ffe27b0abbb","tid":1867983,"uid":169