" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050025001489d788377d9acb1ac4604faea9b635","tid":1867983,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d846b037e5ae2f1e84510520e218e61e6cac87e4","tid":1867983,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於輸<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05601ee6f63102b0be2bb9a93e9aaa0b234faa10","tid":1867983,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"[突發]港龍工會都宣佈要搞罷工啦!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988</a>"},{"pid":"8032bba63837eb1e3cf92d7036d7c477d9154024","tid":1867983,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05601ee6f63102b0be2bb9a93e9aaa0b234faa10","tid":1867983,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"[突發]港龍工會都宣佈要搞罷工啦!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988</a>"},"cited